00:31:43,020 --> 00:31:44,700
If we want
to turn the situation in Macau around,

566
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:48,110
the feud between Master Sanhe
and Rodrigues must be resolved.

567
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,210
I'm an outsider.

568
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:52,330
Perhaps I could have a talk
with Master Sanhe.

569
00:31:52,820 --> 00:31:54,410
I understand, but...

570
00:31:55,270 --> 00:31:57,050
Master Sanhe is furious right now,

571
00:31:57,050 --> 00:31:59,100
and he's still wanted
by the Portuguese Macau government.

572
00:31:59,100 --> 00:32:00,120
I'm not sure

573
00:32:01,330 --> 00:32:02,740
i-if he'll come back.

574
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:05,240
It's alright.

575
00:32:05,710 --> 00:32:06,580
Just tell him

576
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:09,400
that I'll be waiting for him here.

577
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:11,930
Okay.

578
00:32:20,850 --> 00:32:23,400
[Kiang Wu Elementary School]

579
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:29,500
[Purchase government bonds
to protect our country together]

580
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:43,850
Mr. Liang,

581
00:32:43,850 --> 00:32:45,730
the police have completed the closure.

582
00:32:45,730 --> 00:32:47,590
Sorry for the disturbance.

583
00:33:01,520 --> 00:33:02,510
Mr. Liang,

584
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,500
it's Christmas Eve today.

585
00:33:05,300 --> 00:33:07,200
The Saint Dominic's Church is holding

586
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,570
a midnight mass ritual.

587
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:11,740
Governor De Solaire, on behalf
of the Macau government, has invited

588
00:33:11,740 --> 00:33:15,700
representatives from various states
and all sectors of Macau

589
00:33:15,730 --> 00:33:17,060
to attend the ceremony.

590
00:33:17,760 --> 00:33:21,760
This is a personal invitation for you
from His Excellency the Governor.

591
00:33:22,180 --> 00:33:24,980
We hope you will attend, Mr. Liang.

592
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:51,950
[Cultivate virtue and enlighten people]

593
00:33:52,050 --> 00:33:54,400
[Work hard and forge ahead]

594
00:34:16,610 --> 00:34:22,150
[Fundraising Committee Member]

595
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:35,860
Xian.

596
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,600
About what happened yesterday,

597
00:34:42,690 --> 00:34:43,630
it was my fault.

598
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:45,710
I'm sorry.

599
00:34:59,050 --> 00:35:00,860
Keep an eye on the dance hall business.

600
00:35:00,860 --> 00:35:02,190
I won't be back tonight.

601
00:35:02,830 --> 00:35:03,620
Yes, Boss.

602
00:35:04,840 --> 00:35:07,170
But Miss Qiao has been
looking for you several times today.

603
00:35:07,170 --> 00:35:08,380
If she asks me again,

604
00:35:08,400 --> 00:35:09,400
what do I say?

605
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:14,510
Just tell her I'm away on business
for a couple of days.

606
00:35:14,510 --> 00:35:14,860
No,

607
00:35:15,380 --> 00:35:17,240
tell her I won't be back for a week.

608
00:35:19,050 --> 00:35:19,860
Understood.

609
00:35:27,490 --> 00:35:28,450
Miss Qiao?

610
00:35:30,310 --> 00:35:31,710
What on earth is going on?

611
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:35,310
What do you mean?

612
00:35:38,560 --> 00:35:39,880
Such a vague question

613
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:41,860
has me completely confused.

614
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:44,720
You said you'd be the first
to vote against the bans.

615
00:35:44,980 --> 00:35:45,940
Why did you go back on your word

616
00:35:45,940 --> 00:35:47,470
and side with the Japanese?

617
00:35:47,730 --> 00:35:49,760
When did I side with the Japanese?

618
00:35:50,130 --> 00:35:52,280
I just cast an abstention vote.

619
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:55,250
How is that any different
from siding with the Japanese?

620
00:35:55,250 --> 00:35:57,030
All patriotic activities are

621
00:35:57,030 --> 00:35:58,160
banned in Macau now.

622
00:35:58,940 --> 00:36:01,630
Mr. Liang and the students were beaten
by the intelligence agents.

623
00:36:01,630 --> 00:36:02,730
Now, Macau has totally

624
00:36:02,730 --> 00:36:04,050
become a place where the Japanese

625
00:36:04,050 --> 00:36:05,510
can do whatever they want.

626
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:09,190
Why aren't you saying anything,

627
00:36:09,190 --> 00:36:10,050
Dr. Lok Pak?

628
00:36:10,050 --> 00:36:12,090
Do you think
that being a Portuguese citizen

629
00:36:12,090 --> 00:36:14,350
means China's fate doesn't concern you?

630
00:36:25,130 --> 00:36:26,050
Dr. Lok Pak.

631
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,350
Don't forget

632
00:36:31,860 --> 00:36:33,620
that you are also of Chinese descent.

633
00:36:33,620 --> 00:36:35,170
Chinese blood

634
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,260
runs in your veins.

635
00:36:37,570 --> 00:36:39,320
What on earth made you change your mind?

636
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:40,460
Can you tell me?

637
00:36:44,010 --> 00:36:45,510
You really need to know why,

638
00:36:45,510 --> 00:36:46,110
don't you?

639
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:47,980
Yes,

640
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,200
I want to know.

641
00:36:50,700 --> 00:36:51,250
Fine,

642
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,610
I'll tell you.

643
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:54,860
Everything I did was

644
00:36:55,510 --> 00:36:56,420
for your sake.

645
00:37:00,950 --> 00:37:03,280
Why did you come back to Bachongtian Club?

646
00:37:03,380 --> 00:37:05,110
Why did you move into this room?

647
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:06,830
Was it really, as you said,

648
00:37:07,170 --> 00:37:08,130
just for work?

649
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:16,160
Yes, I came back here
because of my brother.

650
00:37:18,020 --> 00:37:19,820
It had nothing to do with He Xian?

651
00:37:21,350 --> 00:37:22,180
He Xian?

652
00:37:23,690 --> 00:37:25,480
You know very well deep down inside

653
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:27,230
whether it had anything to do with him.

654
00:37:27,230 --> 00:37:28,900
Actually, I should have realized earlier.

655
00:37:28,900 --> 00:37:30,750
If you weren't still attached to him,

656
00:37:30,750 --> 00:37:32,270
how could you be so deeply hurt

657
00:37:32,270 --> 00:37:33,400
and care so much?

658
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:35,220
There's nothing going on

659
00:37:35,250 --> 00:37:36,320
between Xian and me.

660
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,370
It's not like what you're imagining.

661
00:37:37,370 --> 00:37:38,830
You don't need to explain.

662
00:37:42,590 --> 00:37:43,170
Yinwan.

663
00:37:45,350 --> 00:37:46,580
You know my feelings

664
00:37:46,910 --> 00:37:47,860
for you.

665
00:37:48,510 --> 00:37:49,570
You can't accept me

666
00:37:50,110 --> 00:37:51,770
because your heart
belongs to someone else.

667
00:37:51,770 --> 00:37:52,770
I accept that.

668
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:54,660
But no matter what,

669
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:56,400
I can't let you risk

670
00:37:56,430 --> 00:37:57,630
your life for others.

671
00:37:58,490 --> 00:38:00,890
I can't just watch you
get yourself killed.

672
00:38:01,500 --> 00:38:02,430
You think

673
00:38:02,810 --> 00:38:04,910
watching every intelligence agent
passing by the door

674
00:38:04,910 --> 00:38:06,470
and eavesdropping on everything they say

675
00:38:06,470 --> 00:38:08,330
will get you useful information?

676
00:38:10,250 --> 00:38:11,590
Do you think they'll never discover you

677
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:13,550
when you're just a wall away?

678
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:16,210
It's still better
than doing nothing, right?

679
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:18,480
Dr. Lok Pak,

680
00:38:18,830 --> 00:38:19,900
I came here

681
00:38:20,710 --> 00:38:22,170
not for any single person.

682
00:38:22,990 --> 00:38:23,630
I'm fulfilling

683
00:38:23,630 --> 00:38:25,590
my duty as a Chinese citizen.

684
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:28,730
That's exactly why I cast
that abstention vote!

685
00:38:30,990 --> 00:38:33,630
Because I can't change
the situation in Macau.

686
00:38:34,780 --> 00:38:37,440
I can't turn bandits
from evil guys to good ones.

687
00:38:37,650 --> 00:38:40,110
I can't force you
to hold back and do nothing.

688
00:38:42,630 --> 00:38:43,360
Perhaps,

689
00:38:44,030 --> 00:38:46,130
only by banning
anti-Japanese protests in Macau

690
00:38:46,130 --> 00:38:47,860
to stop you from doing anything

691
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:50,050
can I finally keep you safe.

692
00:38:51,930 --> 00:38:53,700
I don't need protection!

693
00:38:53,730 --> 00:38:55,380
I don't need this kind of life,
living on my knees!

694
00:38:55,380 --> 00:38:56,480
I don't need it!

695
00:39:02,130 --> 00:39:03,320
I need it.

696
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:13,890
Yinwan,

697
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,540
maybe in this lifetime,

698
00:39:16,540 --> 00:39:18,670
I'll never find my way into your heart,

699
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:21,780
but I will never let anything
happen to you,

700
00:39:21,780 --> 00:39:23,510
especially not under my watch.

701
00:39:26,690 --> 00:39:28,280
Because I, Lok Pak,

702
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:31,800
will always protect the woman
I cherish and love.

703
00:39:41,220 --> 00:39:44,160
I still need to go
to Saint Dominic's Church for the mass.

704
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:45,490
Our conversation today

705
00:39:45,670 --> 00:39:46,400
ends here.

706
00:39:46,940 --> 00:39:49,060
I hope you can stay safe

707
00:39:50,130 --> 00:39:52,390
and stop getting yourself into trouble.

708
00:39:55,050 --> 00:39:56,050
Merry Christmas.

709
00:40:14,570 --> 00:40:16,350
Honestly, everyone can tell

710
00:40:17,680 --> 00:40:19,210
that Miss Qiao has feelings

711
00:40:20,090 --> 00:40:20,900
for you.

712
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:25,700
She went to that treacherous place,
Bachongtian Club,

713
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:28,280
partly because of you, right?

714
00:40:30,800 --> 00:40:31,700
Chang,

715
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:33,730
there's nothing

716
00:40:34,190 --> 00:40:35,720
between Qiao Yinwan and me.

717
00:40:35,950 --> 00:40:36,950
But doesn't that

718
00:40:38,470 --> 00:40:39,930
just add to your pressure?

719
00:40:44,260 --> 00:40:45,440
Just like Mary...

720
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,010
I still can't get over

721
00:40:51,010 --> 00:40:52,320
this guilt inside me.

722
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,650
I got her killed.

723
00:40:59,830 --> 00:41:01,090
If I hadn't helped her,

724
00:41:01,890 --> 00:41:05,150
she couldn't have established
that British Army Service Station.

725
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:06,550
And she wouldn't have...

726
00:41:08,130 --> 00:41:08,820
You always scold me

727
00:41:08,820 --> 00:41:11,980
for drinking myself numb every day
like a mindless zombie.

728
00:41:11,980 --> 00:41:13,110
But if I don't drink,

729
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:15,780
all I see is Mary in her nurse uniform

730
00:41:17,790 --> 00:41:19,450
at the last moment of her life.

731
00:41:23,780 --> 00:41:24,400
Without alcohol,

732
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:26,320
I can't even close my eyes, Xian.

733
00:41:28,780 --> 00:41:29,590
Yes.

734
00:41:31,520 --> 00:41:32,900
Yinwan now is

735
00:41:33,720 --> 00:41:35,530
just like Mary back then,

736
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:37,730
risking their lives

737
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:40,960
to fight right under the Japanese's noses.

738
00:41:52,590 --> 00:41:53,590
Have a drink.

739
00:41:56,380 --> 00:41:58,800
Drink more, and your worries will fade.

740
00:42:08,170 --> 00:42:09,030
Wanqi?

741
00:42:09,720 --> 00:42:10,640
Mr. Ma?

742
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:14,440
Mrs. He told me

743
00:42:16,170 --> 00:42:17,770
that you and Chang were here.

744
00:42:21,690 --> 00:42:22,730
You're sick.

745
00:42:26,030 --> 00:42:26,820
Chang,

746
00:42:27,470 --> 00:42:28,310
let him drink.

747
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:38,730
You already knew it, right?

748
00:42:40,520 --> 00:42:41,850
When I was leaving home,

749
00:42:42,170 --> 00:42:43,510
Qiwen received a call.

750
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:45,090
She said Baixin

751
00:42:45,670 --> 00:42:46,710
returned the wedding dress.
